---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Sáamaka Soul Trust">
	<Header />
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-container">
				<span class="subtitle">My story</span>
				<h1>About me</h1>
				<div class="hero-line"></div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="story">
			<div class="story-container">
				<div class="story-text">
					<p class="lead">
						You know the saying "God only gives his strongest soldiers his hardest battles"...?
					</p>
					<p class="highlight">That's me!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508214751196-bcfd4ca60f91?w=500&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Portrait" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="backstory">
			<div class="backstory-container">
				<div class="backstory-card">
					<p>During those battles I was the black sheep of the family, raising myself and I was a loner.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="backstory-card">
					<p>I really had nobody to turn to! The crazy part about that is that everybody always came to me for everything.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="questions">
			<div class="questions-container">
				<h2>When I was fighting my battles, I kept coming back to 4 questions:</h2>
				<div class="questions-grid">
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">1</span>
						<p>Why do I have to suffer?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">2</span>
						<p>Why is it that, despite everything, I still have so much love to give?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">3</span>
						<p>Why do I long so deeply for love — from family, friends, and a husband — yet have not received it?</p>
					</div>
					<div class="question">
						<span class="number">4</span>
						<p>Why was I always in a struggle just to stay in school?</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="revelation">
			<div class="revelation-container">
				<h2>Now I know!</h2>
				<div class="quotes">
					<blockquote>
						"I have walked the path myself, and now I guide others along the way."
					</blockquote>
					<blockquote>
						"What I have lived through does not make me a victim – it makes me a guide for those who are still on the journey."
					</blockquote>
				</div>
				<p class="signature">Nankurunaisa</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mission">
			<div class="mission-container">
				<h2>Missie & Visie</h2>
				<div class="mission-content">
					<div class="mission-block">
						<div class="mission-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c9a227" stroke-width="1.5">
								<path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Missie</h3>
						<p>Ondersteuning en begeleiding van spirituele, culturele en persoonlijke ontwikkeling.</p>
						<p>Met speciale aandacht voor de Sáamaka gemeenschap en voor ieder mens die zich spiritueel verbindt met aarde, natuur en erfgoed.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mission-block">
						<div class="mission-icon">
							<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c9a227" stroke-width="1.5">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
								<path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Visie</h3>
						<p>Een wereld waarin mensen hun donker durven aankijken, zodat ze hun eigen licht leren ontsteken.</p>
						<p>Mijn merk staat voor waarheid, healing en empowerment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="belief">
			<div class="belief-container">
				<p>Ik geloof dat ware heling ontstaat vanuit verbinding met jezelf, met de natuur, met voorouders en met de community.</p>
				<p class="highlight">De stichting is een brug tussen werelden: tussen oud en nieuw, tussen individueel en collectief, tussen innerlijk weten en praktische actie.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #c9a227;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-line {
		width: 60px;
		height: 1px;
		background-color: #c9a227;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.story {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 4rem;
	}

	.story-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
		gap: 4rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.story-text .lead {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-text .highlight {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #c9a227;
	}

	.story-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.backstory {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 2rem 4rem 4rem;
	}

	.backstory-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.backstory-card {
		padding: 2rem;
		border-left: 2px solid #c9a227;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.05) 0%, transparent 100%);
	}

	.backstory-card p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.questions {
		background-color: #0a0a0a;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
	}

	.questions-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.questions h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.questions-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.question {
		padding: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.question:hover {
		border-color: #c9a227;
	}

	.question .number {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #c9a227;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.question p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.revelation {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.revelation-container {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.revelation h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #c9a227;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.quotes {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.quotes blockquote {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.signature {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #c9a227;
	}

	.mission {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 5rem 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.mission-container {
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.mission h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.mission-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
	}

	.mission-block {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.mission-icon {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.mission-block h3 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #c9a227;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.mission-block p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #a0a0a0;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.belief {
		background-color: #0a0a0a;
		padding: 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.belief-container {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.belief p {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #a0a0a0;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.belief .highlight {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.story {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.story-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.story-image {
			order: -1;
			justify-self: center;
		}

		.story-image img {
			max-width: 280px;
		}

		.story-text {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.story-text .highlight {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.backstory {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.backstory-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.questions {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.questions h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.questions-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.revelation {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.revelation h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.quotes blockquote {
			font-size: 1.15rem;
		}

		.mission {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.mission-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.belief {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
